    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-06-16T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-06-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="1712"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1712">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 850d.00/286.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Delegates</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegrams.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Christiania</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-06-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 16, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Conference convened to-day. Minister Hagerup elected President. Norway, Russia
                    and Sweden submitted amended plan. Conference adjourning for one week to
                    consider it. Copies of plan sent by mail. No other plans or suggestions yet
                    submitted. Gunther appointed Secretary of our delegation.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <list>
                            <item>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Collier</hi>.</item>
                            <item>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Schmedeman</hi>.</item>
                        </list>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
